    <item>
      <title>०१ गार्हपत्यम्</title>
      <link>https://vishvAsa.github.io/vedAH_yajuH/taittirIyam/sArasvata-vibhAgaH/saMhitA/sarva-prastutiH/1/5_punarAdheyAdi/03_punar-AdhAna-mantrAH/01_gArhapatyam/</link>
      <pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
      <guid>https://vishvAsa.github.io/vedAH_yajuH/taittirIyam/sArasvata-vibhAgaH/saMhitA/sarva-prastutiH/1/5_punarAdheyAdi/03_punar-AdhAna-mantrAH/01_gArhapatyam/</guid>
      <description>&lt;details&gt;&lt;summary&gt;भास्करोक्त-विनियोगः&lt;/summary&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;1अथ पुनराधेयमन्त्राः । तत्र गार्हपत्य आधीयमाने सर्पराज्ञीस्तिस्रोनुवर्तयति - भूमिर्भूम्नेति ॥&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;/details&gt;&#xA;&lt;div class=&#34;js_include&#34; newlevelforh1=&#34;4&#34; title=&#34;विश्वास-प्रस्तुतिः&#34; unfilled url=&#34;https://vishvAsa.github.io/vedAH_yajuH/vedAH_yajuH/taittirIyam/sArasvata-vibhAgaH/saMhitA/Rk/vishvAsa-prastutiH/1/5_punarAdheyAdi/03_punar-AdhAna-mantrAH/01_gArhapatyam/02_bhUmir_bhUmnA.md&#34;&gt;&#xA;&lt;details open&gt;&lt;summary&gt;&lt;h4&gt;विश्वास-प्रस्तुतिः ...{Loading}...&lt;/h4&gt;&lt;/summary&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;भूमि॑र् भू॒म्ना+++(=बहुत्वेन)+++, द्यौर् व॑रि॒णा+++(=उरुत्वेन)+++,&lt;br&gt;&#xA;ऽन्तरि॑क्षम् महि॒त्वा +++(असि)+++।&lt;br&gt;&#xA;+++(पुरा वृषभराशौ खे यथा)+++ &lt;strong&gt;उ॒पस्थे॑&lt;/strong&gt; ते देव्य् &lt;strong&gt;अदिते॒&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br&gt;&#xA;+++(सूर्यः खे यथा)+++ &lt;strong&gt;ऽग्निम्&lt;/strong&gt; अ॑न्ना॒दम् अ॒न्नाद्या॒या+++(=अन्नाद-हिताय)+++ &lt;strong&gt;ऽऽद॑धे&lt;/strong&gt;  ॥&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;/details&gt;&#xA;&lt;/div&gt;&#xA;&lt;div class=&#34;js_include&#34; newlevelforh1=&#34;4&#34; title=&#34;सर्वाष् टीकाः&#34; unfilled url=&#34;https://vishvAsa.github.io/vedAH_yajuH/vedAH_yajuH/taittirIyam/sArasvata-vibhAgaH/saMhitA/Rk/sarvASh_TIkAH/1/5_punarAdheyAdi/03_punar-AdhAna-mantrAH/01_gArhapatyam/02_bhUmir_bhUmnA.md&#34;&gt;&#xA;&lt;details open&gt;&lt;summary&gt;&lt;h4&gt;सर्वाष् टीकाः ...{Loading}...&lt;/h4&gt;&lt;/summary&gt;&#xA;&lt;details&gt;&lt;summary&gt;Keith&lt;/summary&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;(Thou art) earth in depth, sky in breadth, atmosphere in greatness;&lt;br&gt;&#xA;In thy lap, O goddess Aditi, Agni&lt;br&gt;&#xA;I place, food-eater for the eating of food.&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;/details&gt;&#xA;&lt;details&gt;&lt;summary&gt;मूलम्&lt;/summary&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;भूमि॑र्भू॒म्ना द्यौर्व॑रि॒णाऽन्तरि॑क्षम्महि॒त्वा ।&lt;br&gt;&#xA;उ॒पस्थे॑ ते देव्यदिते॒ऽग्निम॑न्ना॒दम॒न्नाद्या॒याऽऽद॑धे  ॥&lt;/p&gt;</description>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>०२ आहवनीयम्</title>
      <link>https://vishvAsa.github.io/vedAH_yajuH/taittirIyam/sArasvata-vibhAgaH/saMhitA/sarva-prastutiH/1/5_punarAdheyAdi/03_punar-AdhAna-mantrAH/02_AhavanIyam/</link>
      <pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
      <guid>https://vishvAsa.github.io/vedAH_yajuH/taittirIyam/sArasvata-vibhAgaH/saMhitA/sarva-prastutiH/1/5_punarAdheyAdi/03_punar-AdhAna-mantrAH/02_AhavanIyam/</guid>
      <description>&lt;hr&gt;&#xA;&lt;details&gt;&lt;summary&gt;भास्करोक्त-विनियोगः&lt;/summary&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;4आहवनीये तिस्रोनुवर्तयति । तत्र प्रथमा - अस्येति गायत्री ॥&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;/details&gt;&#xA;&lt;div class=&#34;js_include&#34; newlevelforh1=&#34;4&#34; title=&#34;विश्वास-प्रस्तुतिः&#34; unfilled url=&#34;https://vishvAsa.github.io/vedAH_yajuH/vedAH_yajuH/taittirIyam/sArasvata-vibhAgaH/saMhitA/Rk/vishvAsa-prastutiH/1/5_punarAdheyAdi/03_punar-AdhAna-mantrAH/02_AhavanIyam/02_asya_prANAd.md&#34;&gt;&#xA;&lt;details open&gt;&lt;summary&gt;&lt;h4&gt;विश्वास-प्रस्तुतिः ...{Loading}...&lt;/h4&gt;&lt;/summary&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;अ॒स्य +++(विषूव-सूर्यात्मनो ऽग्नेः)+++ प्रा॒णाद् &lt;strong&gt;अ॑पान॒त्य्&lt;/strong&gt;,&lt;br&gt;&#xA;+++(वृषभराशेर्)+++ &lt;strong&gt;अ॑न्तश् च॑रति&lt;/strong&gt; रोच॒ना+++(→ रोहिणी दीप्तिर् वा)+++ ।&lt;br&gt;&#xA;व्य॑ख्यन्+++(=प्राकाशयन्)+++ महि॒षस् +++(वृषभराशौ सूर्यः, भुव्य् अग्निः)+++ सुवः॑ +++(→दिव॑म् इति शाकले)+++ ॥&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;/details&gt;&#xA;&lt;/div&gt;&#xA;&lt;div class=&#34;js_include&#34; newlevelforh1=&#34;4&#34; title=&#34;सर्वाष् टीकाः&#34; unfilled url=&#34;https://vishvAsa.github.io/vedAH_yajuH/vedAH_yajuH/taittirIyam/sArasvata-vibhAgaH/saMhitA/Rk/sarvASh_TIkAH/1/5_punarAdheyAdi/03_punar-AdhAna-mantrAH/02_AhavanIyam/02_asya_prANAd.md&#34;&gt;&#xA;&lt;details open&gt;&lt;summary&gt;&lt;h4&gt;सर्वाष् टीकाः ...{Loading}...&lt;/h4&gt;&lt;/summary&gt;&#xA;&lt;details&gt;&lt;summary&gt;Keith&lt;/summary&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;With her inspiration from his expiration,&lt;br&gt;&#xA;She wandereth between the worlds;&lt;br&gt;&#xA;The bull discerneth the heaven.&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;/details&gt;&#xA;&lt;details&gt;&lt;summary&gt;मूलम्&lt;/summary&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;अ॒स्य प्रा॒णाद॑पान॒त्य॑न्तश्च॑रति रोच॒ना ।&lt;br&gt;&#xA;व्य॑ख्यन्महि॒षस्सुवः॑  ॥&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;/details&gt;&#xA;&lt;details&gt;&lt;summary&gt;भट्टभास्कर-टीका&lt;/summary&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;अपानतीति प्रथमपादान्तः । अस्याग्नेः &lt;strong&gt;रोचना&lt;/strong&gt; दीप्तिः रोचनशीला । &amp;lsquo;अनुदात्तेतश्च&amp;rsquo; इति युच् । &lt;strong&gt;अन्तश्&lt;/strong&gt; शरीरेषु &lt;strong&gt;चरति&lt;/strong&gt; । किं कुर्वती &lt;strong&gt;प्राणात्&lt;/strong&gt; प्राणनव्यापारात् अनन्तरम् &lt;strong&gt;अपानती&lt;/strong&gt; अपाननव्यापारं कुर्वती । जीवानां ऊर्ध्वगमनं प्राणनं, अधोगमनम् अपाननम् । जीवश्श्वासवायुः ।&lt;/p&gt;</description>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>०३ उपस्थानम्</title>
      <link>https://vishvAsa.github.io/vedAH_yajuH/taittirIyam/sArasvata-vibhAgaH/saMhitA/sarva-prastutiH/1/5_punarAdheyAdi/03_punar-AdhAna-mantrAH/03_upasthAnam/</link>
      <pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
      <guid>https://vishvAsa.github.io/vedAH_yajuH/taittirIyam/sArasvata-vibhAgaH/saMhitA/sarva-prastutiH/1/5_punarAdheyAdi/03_punar-AdhAna-mantrAH/03_upasthAnam/</guid>
      <description>&lt;hr&gt;&#xA;&lt;details&gt;&lt;summary&gt;भास्करोक्त-विनियोगः&lt;/summary&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;7अग्निहोत्रमन्त्राव् उपस्थानार्थौ - तत्र प्रथमा मन इति विराट् ॥&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;/details&gt;&#xA;&lt;div class=&#34;js_include&#34; newlevelforh1=&#34;5&#34; title=&#34;विश्वास-प्रस्तुतिः&#34; unfilled url=&#34;https://vishvAsa.github.io/vedAH_yajuH/vedAH_yajuH/taittirIyam/sArasvata-vibhAgaH/saMhitA/Rk/vishvAsa-prastutiH/1/5_punarAdheyAdi/03_punar-AdhAna-mantrAH/mano_jyotir.md&#34;&gt;&#xA;&lt;details open&gt;&lt;summary&gt;&lt;h5&gt;विश्वास-प्रस्तुतिः ...{Loading}...&lt;/h5&gt;&lt;/summary&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;मनो॒ ज्योति॑र् &lt;strong&gt;जुषता॒म्&lt;/strong&gt;, आज्यव्ँ॒&lt;br&gt;&#xA;विच्छि॑न्नय्ँ &lt;strong&gt;य॒ज्ञँ सम्&lt;/strong&gt; इ॒मन् &lt;strong&gt;द॑धातु&lt;/strong&gt; ।&lt;br&gt;&#xA;&lt;strong&gt;बृह॒स्पति॑स् तनुताम्&lt;/strong&gt; इ॒मन् नो॒,&lt;br&gt;&#xA;विश्वे॑ दे॒वा इ॒ह &lt;strong&gt;मा॑दयन्ताम्&lt;/strong&gt; ॥&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;/details&gt;&#xA;&lt;/div&gt;&#xA;&lt;div class=&#34;js_include&#34; includetitle=&#34;false&#34; newlevelforh1=&#34;5&#34; unfilled url=&#34;https://vishvAsa.github.io/vedAH_yajuH/vedAH_yajuH/taittirIyam/sArasvata-vibhAgaH/saMhitA/Rk/sarvASh_TIkAH/1/5_punarAdheyAdi/03_punar-AdhAna-mantrAH/mano_jyotir.md&#34;&gt;&#xA;&lt;details open&gt;&lt;summary&gt;&lt;h5&gt;मनो ज्योतिर् ...{Loading}...&lt;/h5&gt;&lt;/summary&gt;&#xA;&lt;details&gt;&lt;summary&gt;Keith&lt;/summary&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;Mind, light, rejoice in the oblation.&lt;br&gt;&#xA;May be unite this scattered sacrifice;&lt;br&gt;&#xA;May Brhaspati extend it;&lt;br&gt;&#xA;May the All-gods rejoice herein.&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;/details&gt;&#xA;&lt;details&gt;&lt;summary&gt;मूलम्&lt;/summary&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;मनो॒ ज्योति॑र्जुषता॒माज्यव्ँ॒विच्छि॑न्नय्ँ य॒ज्ञँ समि॒मन्द॑धातु ।&lt;br&gt;&#xA;बृह॒स्पति॑स्तनुतामि॒मन्नो॒ विश्वे॑ दे॒वा इ॒ह मा॑दयन्ताम्  ॥&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;/details&gt;&#xA;&lt;details&gt;&lt;summary&gt;पद-पाठः&lt;/summary&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;मनः॑ । ज्योतिः॑ । जु॒ष॒ता॒म् । आज्य॑म् । विच्छि॑न्न॒मिति॒ वि-छि॒न्न॒म् । य॒ज्ञम् । समिति॑ । इ॒मम् । द॒धा॒तु॒ ॥ बृह॒स्पतिः॑ । त॒नु॒ता॒म् । इ॒मम् । नः॒ । विश्वे॑ । दे॒वाः । इ॒ह । मा॒द॒य॒न्ता॒म् ॥&lt;/p&gt;</description>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>०४ अभितः पुरोडाशम्</title>
      <link>https://vishvAsa.github.io/vedAH_yajuH/taittirIyam/sArasvata-vibhAgaH/saMhitA/sarva-prastutiH/1/5_punarAdheyAdi/03_punar-AdhAna-mantrAH/04_abhitaH_puroDAsham/</link>
      <pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
      <guid>https://vishvAsa.github.io/vedAH_yajuH/taittirIyam/sArasvata-vibhAgaH/saMhitA/sarva-prastutiH/1/5_punarAdheyAdi/03_punar-AdhAna-mantrAH/04_abhitaH_puroDAsham/</guid>
      <description>&lt;hr&gt;&#xA;&lt;details&gt;&lt;summary&gt;भास्करोक्त-विनियोगः&lt;/summary&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;9अभितः पुरोडाशम् आहुतीर् जुहोति पुरस्ताद् उपरिष्टाच् च - पनर् ऊर्जेति द्वाभ्यां गायत्रीभ्याम् ॥&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;/details&gt;&#xA;&lt;div class=&#34;js_include&#34; newlevelforh1=&#34;4&#34; title=&#34;विश्वास-प्रस्तुतिः&#34; unfilled url=&#34;https://vishvAsa.github.io/vedAH_yajuH/vedAH_yajuH/taittirIyam/sArasvata-vibhAgaH/saMhitA/Rk/vishvAsa-prastutiH/1/5_punarAdheyAdi/03_punar-AdhAna-mantrAH/04_abhitaH_puroDAsham/02_punar_UrjA.md&#34;&gt;&#xA;&lt;details open&gt;&lt;summary&gt;&lt;h4&gt;विश्वास-प्रस्तुतिः ...{Loading}...&lt;/h4&gt;&lt;/summary&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;पुन॑र् &lt;strong&gt;ऊ॒र्जा नि व॑र्तस्व॒&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br&gt;&#xA;पुन॑र् अग्न इ॒षा ऽऽयु॑षा ।&lt;br&gt;&#xA;पुन॑र् नᳶ &lt;strong&gt;पाहि&lt;/strong&gt; वि॒श्वतः॑ +++(अंशसः इति कौथुमे)+++ ॥&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;/details&gt;&#xA;&lt;/div&gt;&#xA;&lt;div class=&#34;js_include&#34; newlevelforh1=&#34;4&#34; title=&#34;सर्वाष् टीकाः&#34; unfilled url=&#34;https://vishvAsa.github.io/vedAH_yajuH/vedAH_yajuH/taittirIyam/sArasvata-vibhAgaH/saMhitA/Rk/sarvASh_TIkAH/1/5_punarAdheyAdi/03_punar-AdhAna-mantrAH/04_abhitaH_puroDAsham/02_punar_UrjA.md&#34;&gt;&#xA;&lt;details open&gt;&lt;summary&gt;&lt;h4&gt;सर्वाष् टीकाः ...{Loading}...&lt;/h4&gt;&lt;/summary&gt;&#xA;&lt;details&gt;&lt;summary&gt;Keith&lt;/summary&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;Return with strength, return,&lt;br&gt;&#xA;O Agni, with food and life;&lt;br&gt;&#xA;Again guard us on all sides.&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;/details&gt;&#xA;&lt;details&gt;&lt;summary&gt;मूलम्&lt;/summary&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;पुन॑रू॒र्जा नि व॑र्तस्व॒ पुन॑रग्न इ॒षाऽऽयु॑षा ।&lt;br&gt;&#xA;पुन॑र्नᳶ पाहि वि॒श्वतः॑  ॥&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;/details&gt;&#xA;&lt;details&gt;&lt;summary&gt;भट्टभास्कर-टीका&lt;/summary&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;हे अग्ने ऊर्जा रसेन क्षीरादिना अस्मभ्यं देयेन सह निवर्तस्व पुनरुद्वासितोहमिति सञ्जातमन्युर्वा मय्युपेक्षां मा कार्षीः । इषा अन्नेन आयुषा च सह पुनार्निवर्तस्वेत्येव । उद्वासननिमित्ताच्च पापाद्विश्वतोस्मान्पुनः पाहि रक्ष ॥&lt;/p&gt;</description>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>०५ तृतीयम् आधानम्</title>
      <link>https://vishvAsa.github.io/vedAH_yajuH/taittirIyam/sArasvata-vibhAgaH/saMhitA/sarva-prastutiH/1/5_punarAdheyAdi/03_punar-AdhAna-mantrAH/05_tRtIyam_AdhAnam/</link>
